<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078847" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro <choice><abbr>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissimo</expan></choice> et toto Orbe <choice><abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice>
<lb/>Johanni <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><hi rend="u"><choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>gritudine difficili atque laborios<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></hi> coactus sum res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ponsum usque in hanc diem differre ad humanissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mas <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac <choice><abbr>eruditiss.<hi rend="sup">as</hi></abbr><expan>eruditissimas</expan></choice> <rs key="B_991170515017705501" type="letter">tuas litteras</rs> die 25. pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ti Aprilis conscriptas: quibus me pluribus Tibi obs<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>trinxisti et potissimum <hi rend="u">eleganti</hi> ac ingeniosa solutio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne problematis quod proposueram. Corporis valitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>do non satis firma, vires morbo fract<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in causa
             <lb/>sunt ut animum a studiis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter meam volun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatem per aliquod tempus <hi rend="u">abstrahere debeam</hi>.
             <lb/>Quocirca his meis litteris solum Te certiorem
             <lb/>faciam (quod etiam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stare rogavi eruditis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>simum mihique carissimum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filium</rs> Tuum
             <lb/>ante quindecim dies) nullum amplius adesse
             <lb/>dubium quin <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs> Tuus non advoce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur <add><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs></add> ad publice docendum. <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> mei Mecenates <choice><abbr>Proc.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>Procurator</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1253768439" type="person">Venerius</rs> et <choice><abbr>Proc.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>Procurator</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolus</rs> mihi spem maximam, certam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que de hac re <choice><sic>dederum</sic><corr>dederunt</corr></choice> ita ut brevi sint
             <lb/>eundem <choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> Tuum publice voca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>turi adhoc ut possit suas lectiones inchoare
             <lb/>sub venturi <hi rend="u">Novembris initium</hi>. Ipsi <choice><abbr>Excell:<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice>
<pb facs="1078849" n="2"/>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> nominati rem iam decreverunt
             <lb/>me rogante, instante atque testante <choice><abbr>Doctiss.</abbr><expan>Doctissimi</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnati</rs> Tui sufficientiam atque habilitatem in
             <lb/>omnibus scientiis mathematicis. <hi rend="u">Brevi</hi> suum
             <lb/>decretum proponent <rs type="organisation">Senatui Amplissimo</rs>
<lb/>a quo ut spero ipsorum decretum sine ullo
             <lb/>dubio confirmabitur: hoc autem statim ac effec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum fuerit solemniter vocabitur ipse Celeber<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepos</rs> Tuus, quem maxime salutatum
             <lb/>meo nomine cupio. Interim non dubites Vir
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissime</expan></choice> de eventu felicissimo: siquidem quem pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ponunt Professorem <rs type="organisation">Senatui</rs>, <rs type="organisation">Patavini
                <lb/>Lycei</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> authoritatis et sa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pienti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, senatus nunquam recusat, sed <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tius confirmat. <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmini</rs> tractatum <rs key="biblio_6UBTIJT5" type="biblio">de Mensu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ra Aquarum fluentium</rs>, et <rs key="biblio_CZST2I45" type="biblio">de Fluminum natu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><!--Eintrag in Zotero vervollständigen-->
<lb break="no"/>ra</rs> prima occasione per mercatores <hi rend="u">ad Te mit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam</hi>. Hortatus sum et hortor <choice><abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>ingeniosissimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">filium</rs>
<lb/>tuum ut <hi rend="u">commentariis illustret</hi>, atque augeat
             <lb/>scientiam de Aquarum cursibus, velocitatibus
             <lb/>etc. et hunc in finem ipsi legenda proposui
             <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmini</rs> <rs key="biblio_6UBTIJT5" type="biblio">opera</rs>: qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quum Tu videris nullus
             <pb facs="1078850" n="3"/>
<lb/>dubito quin <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielminianis</rs> longe maiora, atque 
             <lb/>ublimiora Theoremata invenias atque demonstres.
             <lb/>Hanc scientiam colere debebit etiam D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs> Tuus,
             <lb/>qui se parare debet ad docendum, et ad ea saltem
             <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>standa qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stitit magno cum plausu D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Her<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mannus</rs> vester mihi amicitia <choice><abbr>coniunctiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>coniunctissimus</expan></choice>, et quem
             <lb/>una cum <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leibnitio</rs> certiorem feci de
             <lb/>promotione Agnati Tui ad Mathemat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Cathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dram</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinam</rs>. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> Tuus optima
             <lb/><hi rend="u">fruitur</hi> valetudine, studiis mathematicis sponte,
             <lb/>meque rogante atque hortante operam dat
             <lb/>horis matutinis, et pomeridianis, Tibi salutem
             <lb/>plurimam mittit, et <hi rend="u">libentissim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></hi> in hac <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">civitate</rs>
<lb/>moratur, ubi ut meos Mecenates aliquando invisat
             <lb/>efficio, ipsisque ipsum commendare non desino.</p>
<p><rs key="biblio_W232JMTP" type="biblio">Opus de Nutritione</rs><!--EK: prüfen ob es sich hier um Hanharts Dissertation handelt--> quod tanta generositate iam
         <lb/>misisti avide expecto, quod postquam legero Tibi
         <lb/>restituam. Cetera scripta Tua secretiora, et subli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>miora <hi rend="u">mittere poteris</hi> per <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> Tuum.
         <lb/>Tandem rogo ut salutes meo nomine D. Agnatum
         <lb/>Tuum <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Nicolaum</rs> <hi rend="u">Pictorem</hi> mihi amicissimum.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale
         <lb/>meque amare perge.</salute>
<dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1716-06-06">6 Junii
            <lb/>1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. Responsio <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnati</rs> Tui<note type="internal">Annahme: Nicolaus I Bernoulli, nicht der Maler. Prüfen!</note> ad Comitem Jacobum <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Ric<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>catum</rs> inserta iam est Diarii Veneti<!-- sachtag --> Tomo XXIII.</p></postscript>
</div></body></text></TEI>